Description:
Pinball FX2 is an ever-growing collection of original pinball table
simulations built by Zen Studios, the world's premier virtual pinball
developer. Pinball FX2 pairs classic pinball gameplay with themes from Star
Wars, Marvel and more. Pick and choose the tables you like from a selection
of dozens - there's something for everyone! Meticulously constructed in
painstaking detail, each table is instantly approachable yet offers dozens
of hours of replay value. You'll need all the practice you can get to
defeat your friends' high scores and earn the title of Pinball King.

wow

Notes:
This game gets updated periodically, and adds new tables and content in
every update. Full game is included, as update would be almost the same
size. As you can see on steam this game is free, but tables are so
expensive. All of them are included in the release. Wow.
